{"tid":1006884,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"周杰倫邀請咖哩仔睇個唱：will give u my mic","createTime":"2019-02-03T10:38:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-03T12:11:10.000Z","uid":147522,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9dfa8d1413060cafe5ca5b81f56963f994f3c9c3","tid":1006884,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T10:38:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ebnj0VE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Febnj0VE.png&h=352c3570&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n周杰倫與昆凌出名是NBA球星「咖哩仔」Stephen Curry的fans，二人於當地時間周六到美國加州Oracle Arena看勇士主場對湖人的NBA常規賽，勇士以115:101戰勝湖人，外父Patrick Quinlivan亦有同行，昆凌稱爸爸是第一次到場看NBA賽，她於Ig貼出與咖哩仔的合照，相中見昆凌猶如小fans，站在偶像身邊有些不知所措，忍不住流露出笑容，她讚比賽一如既往般精彩激烈。<br />\n<br />\n早前咖哩仔於網上「邀請」昆凌到勇士主場看球賽，周杰倫今次禮尚往來邀請咖哩仔看他的演唱會，留言：「如果你來我拉斯維加斯演唱會(2月9至10日)，請告訴我，我會給你我的Mic。」<br />\n<br />\n之前他們兩夫妻已為咖哩仔爭風吃醋，2019年NBA明星賽進行投票時，昆凌曾在社交網為勇士隊一哥咖哩仔拉票加油，指對方是她最喜歡的NBA球員，未想到這個留言，意外獲得咖哩仔回覆：「謝謝你的支持，希望很快能在勇士主場看到你。」身為fans的周杰倫即吃醋：「為甚麼是標記你不是我！」他們之後更分別穿上最新款式的Curry 6第六代籃球鞋，支持偶像。"},{"pid":"be781baf40fe20979f0b0d52e4a999511943422d","tid":1006884,"uid":10895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T10:56:21.000Z","msg":"Curry同佢老婆又幾襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6928551ef446d7c0d79f760a87ea8932769c2f8b","tid":1006884,"uid":294,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T11:07:27.000Z","msg":"依周杰倫個個演唱會都比咪觀眾大合唱架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f53015018b017d29ab1027d6ae7f7b6968ab972","tid":1006884,"uid":1166,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6928551ef446d7c0d79f760a87ea8932769c2f8b","tid":1006884,"uid":294,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T11:07:27.000Z","msg":"依周杰倫個個演唱會都比咪觀眾大合唱架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T12:11:10.000Z","msg":"去到高音位或唔記得歌詞果陣<br />\n就遞個咪畀Curry<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}